{"tid":484064,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"支那人簡直係人類公敵","createTime":"2017-11-29T17:43:52.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-29T18:29:04.000Z","uid":72638,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"dab958b568bb123a17cef17e11e86a0b7f42116d","tid":484064,"uid":72638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T17:43:52.000Z","msg":"又四圍移民炒貴哂啲樓<br />\n令當地人成世人買唔起結唔到婚<br />\n又四圍同當地人爭學位爭職位<br />\n又冇文化 貪污 走後門 大聲講野<br />\n自私四圍屙屎吐痰<br />\n美軍應該掉幾粒核彈去幾個支那大城巿<br />\n死番十億八億 再殺哂呢係世界各地個啲支那人就啱"},{"pid":"630db03d4dd7afcb46f3ef6aee47f8367371f145","tid":484064,"uid":87506,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T17:45:30.000Z","msg":"支持美國以國家名義殺人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea62d48a9892142805821a647da76e141613a75e","tid":484064,"uid":72638,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T17:47:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>支持美國以國家名義殺人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n美軍來了我帶路<br />\n北上橫渡深圳河<br />\n大開殺戒"},{"pid":"c04689d5902946d6ae1966e23c62e0a66e23e474","tid":484064,"uid":72638,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T17:49:45.000Z","msg":"仲要支持北韓政權<br />\n害死千萬無辜的人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc65a09b6f3269ede15a0dcaa54f71fb1512fe6a","tid":484064,"uid":72638,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T17:52:07.000Z","msg":"愈來愈唔妥啲支那畜<br />\n我屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64a21dd4d4a47517447586a49589cb97ffa3dc0c","tid":484064,"uid":72638,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T17:53:48.000Z","msg":"支那